es.uam.eps.ir.ranksys.fast.feature

Interface FastFeatureData<I,F,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - type of the items
    F - type of the features
    V - type of the information about item-feature pairs
    All Superinterfaces:
    FastFeatureIndex<F>, FastItemIndex<I>, FeatureData<I,F,V>, FeatureIndex<F>, ItemIndex<I>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFastFeatureData, SimpleFastFeatureData

    public interface FastFeatureData<I,F,V>
extends FeatureData<I,F,V>, FastItemIndex<I>, FastFeatureIndex<F>
    Fast version of FeatureData, where item-feature relationships are stored internally by the indexes provided by FastItemIndex and FastFeatureIndex.
    Author:
    Sa√∫l Vargas (saul.vargas@uam.es)
